"{\"uid\": \"inews.co.uk-news-man-scaling-eiffel-tower-before-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-3221784\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"IMPARTIAL NEWS + INTELLIGENT DEBATE  Account  20,000 police troops and security personnel will be in place in the Saint-Denis area of Paris ahead of the last day of the Olympics  A shirtless man attempted to scale the Eiffel Tower, prompting authorities to evacuate the Paris landmark only hours before theOlympics closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 134, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995347935, \"rank\": 4.653124143059795e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995347935, \"rank\": 4.653124143059795e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The man was seen climbing the330-metre toweron Sunday afternoon but French police said they \\\"immediately intervened and arrested\\\" him.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.005621658873763e-23, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police escorted visitors away from the area at around 3 pm.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In one video posted to social media, he can be seen smiling, saying to bystanders \\\"Bloody warm, innit?\\\"\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"in what appears to be a British accent, as he is escorted off the viewing platform by police.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_English\", \"score\": 0.9985539023952725, \"rank\": 0.001446414256449145, \"text\": \"British accent\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_English\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_English\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Videos posted on social media showed the rogue climber navigating the Olympic rings.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was unclear where he began his ascent but he was spotted above the Olympic rings sitting on the structure, just above the first viewing deck.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police escorted visitors away from the area and the entry beneath the tower was closed.\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some visitors were briefly locked in on the second floor but were allowed to exit around 30 minutes later.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson for Paris police said: \\\"An individual started climbing the\\u00a0Eiffel\\u00a0Tower\\u00a0at 2.45pm, police intervened and the person was detained.\\\"\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1177, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995347935, \"rank\": 4.653124143059795e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 30,000 police officers have been deployed around Paris with France's Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin saying about 3,000 police officers will be mobilised around the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso